Element


keysym
&keysym.purpose;


&keysym.synopsis.gen;
Description



The KeySym identifies the symbolic name of a key on a 
computer keyboard. This is distinct from any scan code
that it may generate (KeyCode), or any symbolic name
(KeySym) that might exist for the key.


